486	[Clicked: admission_procedure]	\n    The admission process usually follows these steps:\n\n    a. NEW STUDENT\n    Step 1. Access this link: http://lcc-silvercrest.com\n    - Fill out online application form\n    - Fill up the online form accurately then click Submit Application\n    - Wait for the acknowledgement of admission office for the next step\n    Step 2. Go to Guidance & Admission Office for assessment.\n    - Once approved you can now proceed to next step\n    Step 3. Enlistment and printing of pre-assessment\n    - Go to the designated location of the department office of your chosen program\n    - This is were you will submit every requirements you have\n    - Once approved, Assessment Form will be given and you can now proceed to next step\n    Step 3. Payment\n    - Pay the initial fees (upon enrollment) or the full payment.\n    - Pay online by going to http://lcc-silvercrest.com/paydp wherein you can use Paymaya, GCash, \n    Coins.ph,7/11 and other payment methods. You may also pay in the accounting office at the \n    Main Building (2nd Floor Windows 2 and 3).\n    Step 4. Lms Enrollment\n    - Student's LMS user name and password to be sent via email by the LMS Office.\n    - Log-in your LMS Account thru: https://lcc-welearn.neolms.com/ using your username and \n    password on the opening of classes.\n    b. OLD STUDENTS\n    1. Accomplish pre-registration form and present to the Dean for evaluation and approval.\n    2. Proceed to the Registrar’s office for encoding of data.\n    3. Pay the required fees at the Cashier’s Office.\n    4. Surrender the Old ID for issuance of a new one.\n    	admission_procedure	100	2026-03-07 14:59:17.550211+08	\N
