676	how long is the program	Great question about program duration! 📅\n\n**Most of our programs are 4-year degrees** (8 semesters of study).\n\nThis includes:\n• **All Business programs** (BSBA, BSA, BSMA) - 4 years\n• **Education programs** (BEED, BSED) - 4 years  \n• **Nursing** (BSN) - 4 years\n• **Criminology** (BSCRIM) - 4 years\n• **Computer Science/Engineering** (BSCS, BSCPE) - 4 years\n• **Hospitality & Tourism** (BSHM, BSTM) - 4 years\n• **Psychology** (AB-PSY) - 4 years\n\n**That's 8 semesters total** - you'll study 5-6 months per semester, with summer breaks in between!\n\nSome programs might have practicum or internship requirements in your final year, which adds valuable hands-on experience!\n\nWhich specific program are you interested in? I can tell you more about what you'll study! 😊	program_duration	69.93821324788614	2026-03-28 23:46:08.009347+08	\N
