791	What to submit?	Perfect! Let me help you prepare the documents you'll need!\n\n<strong>IF YOU'RE AN INCOMING FRESHMAN (from senior high school):</strong>\n\nYou'll need to bring these:\n<strong>1.</strong> <strong>Form 138</strong> (your report card)\n<strong>2.</strong> <strong>Form 137</strong> (permanent record)\n<strong>3.</strong> <strong>Certificate of Good Moral Character</strong>\n<strong>4.</strong> <strong>PSA Birth Certificate</strong> (the original from PSA, not just a photocopy)\n<strong>5.</strong> <strong>Three 2x2 ID photos</strong> (recent, with white background)\n<strong>6.</strong> <strong>Program-specific requirements</strong> (some courses might need additional documents)\n\nYou'll also need to:\n<strong>1.</strong> <strong>Take the entrance examination</strong>\n<strong>2.</strong> <strong>Attend an admission interview</strong>\n\n<strong>IF YOU'RE A TRANSFEREE (from another school):</strong>\nBring these documents:\n<strong>1.</strong> <strong>Transcript of Records (TOR)</strong>\n<strong>2.</strong> <strong>Certificate of Eligibility to Transfer</strong> (if applicable)\n<strong>3.</strong> <strong>Certificate of Good Moral Character</strong>\n<strong>4.</strong> <strong>PSA Birth Certificate</strong>\n<strong>5.</strong> <strong>2-3 pieces of 2x2 ID photos</strong>\n\nDon't worry! The Registrar will help evaluate which of your previous courses are creditable here at LCC.\n\nDo you need help with anything else? Like the admission procedure or enrollment schedule? Just let me know!	admission_requirements	69.33479325314688	2026-03-30 16:18:32.91452+08	\N
794	Years needed?	Great question about program duration!\n\n<strong>Most of our programs are 4-year degrees (8 semesters of study).</strong>\n<strong>This includes:</strong>\n<strong>1.</strong> <strong>Business programs (BSBA, BSA, BSMA)</strong> - 4 years  \n<strong>2.</strong> <strong>Education programs (BEED, BSED)</strong> - 4 years  \n<strong>3.</strong> <strong>Nursing (BSN)</strong> - 4 years  \n<strong>4.</strong> <strong>Criminology (BSCRIM)</strong> - 4 years  \n<strong>5.</strong> <strong>Computer Science and Engineering (BSCS, BSCPE)</strong> - 4 years  \n<strong>6.</strong> <strong>Hospitality and Tourism (BSHM, BSTM)</strong> - 4 years  \n<strong>7.</strong> <strong>Psychology (AB-PSY)</strong> - 4 years  \n\n<strong>That's 8 semesters total</strong> - you'll study 5 to 6 months per semester, with breaks in between.\n\nSome programs may include <strong>practicum or internship requirements</strong> in the final year, giving you valuable hands-on experience.\n\nWhich specific program are you interested in? I can tell you more about what you'll study!	program_duration	68.43229793680868	2026-03-30 16:19:03.453708+08	\N
