83	Absolutely! Let me tell you about the Employee Privilege!\n\n<strong>WHAT IS IT:</strong>  \nThe Employee Privilege is a tuition discount granted to the legitimate spouse and children of LCC employees.\n\n<strong>WHO CAN QUALIFY:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> Legitimate spouse of an LCC employee  \n<strong>2.</strong> Children of an LCC employee  \n<strong>3.</strong> Applies to both regular or permanent and probationary employees  \n\n<strong>SCHOLARSHIP BENEFITS:</strong>  \n\n<strong>FOR REGULAR OR PERMANENT EMPLOYEES:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> Spouse or first child to enroll - 40% tuition fee discount  \n<strong>2.</strong> Second child to enroll - 30% tuition fee discount  \n<strong>3.</strong> Third child to enroll - 20% tuition fee discount  \n\n<strong>FOR PROBATIONARY EMPLOYEES:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> First and second child to enroll - 15% tuition fee discount  \n\n<strong>WHAT IT COVERS:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> Tuition fee only  \n<strong>2.</strong> Does not include miscellaneous fees  \n\n<strong>DURATION:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> Renewable as long as the employee remains actively employed at LCC  \n\n<strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> Secure an Employee Privilege Form from the Scholarships or HR Office  \n<strong>2.</strong> Complete the form  \n<strong>3.</strong> Submit within the prescribed period  \n\n<strong>RENEWAL REQUIREMENTS:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> Employee must still be actively employed  \n<strong>2.</strong> Submit the Employee Privilege Form each renewal period  \n\n<strong>WHERE TO APPLY:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> Scholarships Office  \n<strong>2.</strong> Human Resources Office  \n\n<strong>EXAMPLE SAVINGS:</strong>  \n<strong>1.</strong> If tuition is ₱20,000:  \n<strong>2.</strong> First child pays ₱12,000 (40% discount)  \n<strong>3.</strong> Second child pays ₱14,000 (30% discount)  \n<strong>4.</strong> Third child pays ₱16,000 (20% discount)  \n\n<strong>NOTE:</strong>  \nThis program is designed to support the families of LCC employees and provide additional educational opportunities.\n\nWould you like to know about other scholarships or discounts? Just ask!	t	2026-03-29 20:22:17.880414+08	2026-03-29 20:39:33.256441+08	98	f		\N	["What is Employee Privilege?", "Discount for LCC employees", "LCC staff discount", "Faculty discount LCC", "Ano ang Employee Privilege?", "Employee Privilege requirements", "How to get Employee Privilege?", "Discount para sa pamilya ng empleyado", "LCC employee family discount", "Child of LCC employee discount", "Spouse of LCC employee discount", "Employee Privilege benefits", "Paano makakuha ng Employee Privilege?", "Employee Privilege details", "What is discount for employee families?", "May discount ba para sa anak ng guro?", "Teacher's child discount LCC", "Staff child scholarship LCC", "Employee Privilege application", "Regular employee discount LCC"]	\N	\N	2026-03-29 20:22:17.880414+08	\N
