iplinary records  \n<strong>4.</strong> Represent LCC in performances and competitions as required  \n\n<strong>NOTE:</strong>  \nThis scholarship allows students to develop their artistic talents while receiving educational support.\n\nFor complete and updated details, visit the Scholarships Office or Student Affairs Office.\n\nWould you like to know about other scholarships available? Just ask!	t	2026-03-29 20:22:17.911573+08	2026-03-29 20:41:41.970264+08	101	f		\N	["What is Cultural Scholarship?", "Performing arts scholarship LCC", "Cultural arts scholarship", "Scholarship for dancers", "Ano ang Cultural Scholarship?", "Scholarship for singers", "How to get cultural scholarship?", "Music scholarship LCC", "Dance scholarship LCC", "Theater scholarship LCC", "Performing arts discount LCC", "Scholarship para sa mananayaw", "LCC cultural scholar", "Cultural scholarship benefits", "Paano makakuha ng cultural scholarship?", "Arts scholarship LCC", "What is arts scholarship in LCC?", "May scholarship ba para sa mang-aawit?", "Cultural scholarship application", "LCC cultural arts performer scholarship"]	\N	\N	2026-03-29 20:22:17.911573+08	\N
